subject: Sailboats and Sailing
Volvo Ocean Race
lead_paragraph: The Dutch skipper Bouwe Bekking executed a masterly passing maneuver to guide Team Brunel to a 16-minute victory in the second leg of the Volvo Ocean Race after 23 days on the open seas.
